{"tid":280660,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[又是押井守]推介套動畫電影-The Sky Crawlers青空之行者","createTime":"2017-06-12T08:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T11:02:03.000Z","uid":8307,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"869dc4225e3f4315c51829120dd5b06a75b30194","tid":280660,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:47:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/a/aa/The_Sky_Crawlers_Cover.jpg/220px-The_Sky_Crawlers_Cover.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fthumb%2Fa%2Faa%2FThe_Sky_Crawlers_Cover.jpg%2F220px-The_Sky_Crawlers_Cover.jpg&h=b205d747&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢套野係香港上過，不過應該冇咩人睇過<br />\n<br />\n故事內容比較需要思考同留意細節，就咁睇落去會覺得好沉悶完全唔知佢做緊咩。<br />\n但當睇到後半段，有個叫三矢既角色講個一返說話好似就明明地，結果我重睇左一次。<br />\n似係一套藝術片 多過似一套戰爭片，對白又冇咩 空戰場景都係得幾場。<br />\n<br />\n比個概念比大家先，<br />\n係故事地點設定有啲似二戰時既歐洲，有無線電技術但唔先進，有打字機式既電腦，科技比較算係落後。<br />\n<br />\n世界上有兩間公司不斷舉辦戰爭show比啲市民睇，令大家知道戰爭既可怕為目的，但其實似係娛樂節目多啲，又會約好幾時空襲等等。<br />\n基因改造左啲細蚊仔永遠長唔大唔會死維持係十幾歲左右，叫佢地駕駛引擎式戰鬥機同對面公司打杖，只要戰場上生存落黎就可以永生。<br />\n<br />\n故事既主人公函南優一，就係呢個成個佐助頭咁樣既男仔，因為佢正正係火影動畫既人物設計師&mdash;西尾鐵也筆下既角色黎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/QYjlUm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FQYjlUm.jpg&h=36529ee5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就話呢條友有日比人排左去兔離洲基地，就話上手個駕駛員死左，但係架飛機留左係到覺得好奇怪，人人又好似識佢咁。<br />\n為呢件事有啲苦惱，之後既事就自己睇啦。<br />\n佢有點完煙啪火柴既習慣。<br />\n<br />\n畫面方面人物就唔係好靚，細節都畫得冇咩，例如衣服上面既徽章得個外框，人物色彩比較平淡單一，有唔少既靜止作畫。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.giphy.com/v2WwmWhYTyQRW.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.giphy.com%2Fv2WwmWhYTyQRW.webp&h=db32ff0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過空戰場面既CG畫面絕對唔遜色，咩啲海水好勁既元素都有。<br />\n<img src=\"http://iv1.lisimg.com/image/7431877/500full-the-sky-crawlers-screenshot.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fiv1.lisimg.com%2Fimage%2F7431877%2F500full-the-sky-crawlers-screenshot.jpg&h=1a1fc3b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n音樂方面都係由押井守最出名個套攻殼機動隊 鬼佬in the shell既川井憲次擔當，首成日重複既BGM既前奏都好有傀儡謠既feel。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1i0643HZjkY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1i0643HZjkY&d=NluVYqOvIRw1lkx15rDVj7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=3fefc428\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1i0643HZjkY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇完之後真係好想好想好想叫春好壓抑。<br />\n永無止境既輪迴下，竟然講得出：<br />\n就算係每日行過無數次既路，都係會行到去未踏足過既地方<br />\n正因為係行過無數次既路，先會有唔同既景色<br />\n唔通咁樣仲唔足夠？<br />\n因為只係咁樣，所以先唔足夠？<br />\n<br />\n點解可以咁樂觀<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-lJyuJnsWV8U/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAQ8/pXe6d-SmKZo/photo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2F-lJyuJnsWV8U%2FAAAAAAAAAAI%2FAAAAAAAAAQ8%2FpXe6d-SmKZo%2Fphoto.jpg&h=31395716&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a9a0e4480c02fe250f93873ecbc6273b0e6388b","tid":280660,"uid":5914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:51:28.000Z","msg":"有點完煙啪火柴既習慣？"},{"pid":"40606e8cb37e23d854dd1eaa78dede850e540988","tid":280660,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:52:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有點完煙啪火柴既習慣？</blockquote><br />\n拎火柴點著枝煙<br />\n點煙個點<br />\n之後啪彎枝火柴"},{"pid":"07b048b9787388adb0fb214fdeacc080636f89a6","tid":280660,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1751f673081c62c64e4554296b4616844325d3b2","tid":280660,"uid":5914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:55:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有點完煙啪火柴既習慣？</blockquote><br />\n拎火柴點著枝煙<br />\n點煙個點<br />\n之後啪彎枝火柴</blockquote><br />\n呢個位有乜特別？"},{"pid":"93b12994b69b92fd754c60c15da162f5a63019d1","tid":280660,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:55:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>